      funder, sponsor, or beneficiary.

  (f) Any deployment that, directly or indirectly, supports or enables
      a revenue-generating activity, a commercial product or service,
      or operations of a paying customer.

The Licensor offers **no no-fee tier** for any of the uses in this
Section. Commercial licences are paid, and pricing depends on scope,
